Color of freshly collected holotype (
Fig. 9
): head and body yellow, scales on dorsal half of body with greenish yellow centers, scales on ventral half of head and body outlined with orangish-yellow; tip of snout orangish yellow; dorsal fin yellow, tips of spines 5–10 magenta, distal margin of soft dorsal with narrow magenta margin; caudal fin yellow with magenta dorsal and ventral margins, anal fin yellow with magenta margin; pelvic fins yellow with magenta anterior margin; pectoral fins yellow; orbit with narrow yellow border, iris yellow with broken outer magenta ring.
